</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:p>A minor change is that the <fr:code>assets</fr:code> directly does not need to be flat anymore.</fr:p><fr:p>As always, existing forests can be upgraded by copying <fr:code>forest.xsl</fr:code> and <fr:code>style.css</fr:code> into their <fr:code>assets</fr:code> directory. </fr:p></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree></fr:context><fr:related><fr:tree
